                &lt;div&gt;
                    
                        &lt;article&gt;
                            &lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/releases/tag/v7.0.0"&gt;v7.0.0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
                            &lt;div&gt;
                                &lt;p&gt;Version 7.0.0 is a major increment due to some changes in the target frameworks and some behavioral changes. &lt;a href="https://autofac.readthedocs.io/en/latest/whats-new/upgradingfrom6to7.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;We summarize these in the documentation&lt;/a&gt;, but included here as well:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;New Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Properties marked &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt; will now be injected by default.&lt;/strong&gt; As part of this, the default property injector using &lt;code&gt;PropertiesAutowired()&lt;/code&gt; will &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; inject properties marked &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt;. &lt;a href="https://autofac.readthedocs.io/en/latest/register/prop-method-injection.html#required-properties" rel="nofollow"&gt;The documentation has more explanation with examples.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ability to isolate &lt;code&gt;AssemblyLoadContext&lt;/code&gt; by lifetime scope.&lt;/strong&gt; A new method, &lt;code&gt;BeginLoadContextLifetimeScope&lt;/code&gt;, has been added that allows you to create a lifetime scope tied to a specific &lt;code&gt;AssemblyLoadContext&lt;/code&gt;. When the scope is disposed, Autofac will perform a best-effort release of all references to types from that context so the assemblies can be unloaded. &lt;a href="https://autofac.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced/scopes-loadcontexts.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;The documentation explains this in greater detail.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation links in exception messages.&lt;/strong&gt; Common Autofac exceptions now include links to &lt;a href="https://autofac.readthedocs.io/en/latest/troubleshooting/index.html#exceptions" rel="nofollow"&gt;our online documentation&lt;/a&gt; to help you understand what the exceptions mean and how to troubleshoot them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Issues and PRs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add documentation links to common exceptions by &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/tillig/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/tillig"&gt;@tillig&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1495295255" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1359" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/pull/1359/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/pull/1359"&gt;#1359&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1518089321" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1360" data-hovercard-type="issue" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/issues/1360/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1360"&gt;#1360&lt;/a&gt;: Unify the "no constructors found" reporting by &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/tillig/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/tillig"&gt;@tillig&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1519527615" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1362" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/pull/1362/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/pull/1362"&gt;#1362&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add support for required properties by &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/alistairjevans/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/alistairjevans"&gt;@alistairjevans&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1560807875" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1364" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/pull/1364/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/pull/1364"&gt;#1364&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mark RegisterGeneratedFactory obsolete by &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/tillig/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/tillig"&gt;@tillig&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1571117725" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1366" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/pull/1366/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/pull/1366"&gt;#1366&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Isolate service information computed in child scopes from the parent scope by &lt;a class="user-mention notranslate" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/alistairjevans/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/alistairjevans"&gt;@alistairjevans&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1386478604" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/issues/1350" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/autofac/Autofac/pull/1350/hovercard" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/pull/1350"&gt;#1350&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Changelog&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a class="commit-link" href="https://github.com/autofac/Autofac/compare/v6.5.0...v7.0.0"&gt;&lt;tt&gt;v6.5.0...v7.0.0&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Breaking Changes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;net50&lt;/code&gt; no longer targeted.&lt;/strong&gt; Autofac will still work with .NET 5 via the &lt;code&gt;netstandard2.1&lt;/code&gt; target, but we recommend you upgrade to a later, supported version of .NET.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Properties marked &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt; will now be injected by default.&lt;/strong&gt; As noted above, &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt; properties will be injected. This is a behavioral change from Autofac 6.0.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Default property injection ignores &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt; properties.&lt;/strong&gt; Using &lt;code&gt;PropertiesAutowired()&lt;/code&gt; will ignore &lt;code&gt;required&lt;/code&gt; properties because it's assumed they must be set during construction rather than post-object-creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;RegisterGeneratedFactory&lt;/code&gt; is obsolete.&lt;/strong&gt; This feature has been replaced by the &lt;code&gt;Func&amp;lt;X, Y, B&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; built-in relationship and delegate factories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;ILifetimeScope&lt;/code&gt; has a new &lt;code&gt;BeginLoadContextLifetimeScope&lt;/code&gt; method.&lt;/strong&gt; If you have mocks of &lt;code&gt;ILifetimeScope&lt;/code&gt; this method must now be implemented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
                            &lt;/div&gt;
                        &lt;/article&gt;
                    
